I feel he couldn't make the paper effigy.

23
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,480
No need to investigate further, Hong.

24
00:03:12,720 --> 00:03:14,960
The paper effigy and Loong

25
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:16,560
